{"tid":355494,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人天生體能好差？會唔會係有病？","createTime":"2017-08-11T10:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T10:59:15.000Z","uid":67407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"753572d1d70aed6f54ed91d650999908f46257b5","tid":355494,"uid":67407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:33:04.000Z","msg":"由細到大都有做開運動，中學仲要打過校隊，但就唔知點解體能好差，會唔會係天生有病？<br />\n<br />\n屋企人好似話過我有貧血唔知關唔關事，但我落醫務所驗又話我無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會有貧血唔係咁易驗出來？"},{"pid":"40f5ef3e150032bfe08a25898ec8c8382761823a","tid":355494,"uid":91875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:34:05.000Z","msg":"乒乓波校隊？"},{"pid":"83c3d339a93dfd942c03896f620d7841564f3b7b","tid":355494,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00a203110ee5c283e491ffec6f88c86618f1fea8","tid":355494,"uid":9269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乒乓波校隊？</blockquote><br />\n我妻d幽默感完全無進步過"},{"pid":"5bff6122c8cd3291f364901ef7430a556fa3e635","tid":355494,"uid":67407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老會退化 人地專業球員過左35歲都回塘啦  你叫列貝利都爆唔起</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我都係得廿幾歲，同埋我中學已經好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以只可以做後備"},{"pid":"2b4b854e58dcbb16e9b5fdfac00b1c707f3666a1","tid":355494,"uid":14899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:58:36.000Z","msg":"跑步練下體能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70059f874a9f35ea460987fad3956e369c95e02","tid":355494,"uid":77705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:59:15.000Z","msg":"體能差可以係心肺功能差/肌肉唔夠<br />\n又或者係運動發力既方法唔正確<br />\n上述既都可以改善<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n廋底都可以練大隻<br />\n哮喘都可以跑到長課<br />\n係要比其他人努力啲啫<br />\n唔好下下都賴天資"}]}